==争议==
美國創作歌手[[泰勒·斯威夫特|泰勒絲]]获得「最佳女歌手音樂錄影帶獎」，但在她发表获奖感言时，饒舌歌手[[肯伊·威斯特|肯伊·威斯特]]突然冲上舞台、抢过泰勒絲手中的话筒、大叫道：“泰勒絲，我为你感到高兴，我等下会让你把话说完，不过，[[碧昂絲|碧昂絲]]的音乐錄影带是史上最棒的！史上最棒的！”（Yo Taylor,  I'm really happy for you and I'm 'a let you finish, but Beyoncé had one of the best videos of all time. One of the best videos of all time.），引起观众一片嘘声。此事後在後台，泰勒絲、泰勒絲的母親及碧昂絲因為此事難過痛哭。之後當碧昂絲獲得「年度音樂錄影帶獎」時，她邀請泰勒絲一起上台獲頒這個獎項，以安慰泰勒絲的心情。後來威斯特在推特上向泰勒絲道歉。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1621389/kanye-west-crashes-vma-stage-during-taylor-swifts-award-speech.jhtml |title=Kanye West Crashes VMA Stage During Taylor Swift's Award Speech - MTV<!-- 机器人生成的标题 --> |accessdate=2011-05-01 |archive-date=2014-09-12 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20140912071844/http://www.mtv.com/news/1621389/kanye-west-crashes-vma-stage-during-taylor-swifts-award-speech/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

此后又传出一段没有放出的CNBC对美国总统[[奥巴马|奥巴马]]的采访录像，奥巴马对此事发表了评论，他说他看到泰勒絲得奖时为她感到高兴，不过，“他（威斯特）冲上去干什么？（what's he doing up there?） 他真是一个蠢驴（He's a jackass）”。再次引起哗然。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1213541/Barack-Obama-calls-Kanye-West-jackass-Kayne-tearfully-apologises-Jay-Leno-MTV-outburst.html |title=Barack Obama calls Kanye West a 'jackass' as Kayne tearfully apologises to Jay Leno after MTV outburst {{!}} Daily Mail Online<!-- 机器人生成的标题 --> |accessdate=2011-05-01 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109041138/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1213541/Barack-Obama-calls-Kanye-West-jackass-Kayne-tearfully-apologises-Jay-Leno-MTV-outburst.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

